com.intel.icecp.core.metadata

Class Frequency

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.icecp.core.metadata.Frequency
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message, Metadata, Serializable

    public class Frequency
extends Object
implements Metadata
    Define the frequency for retrieving messages from a channel. This represents a contract from the Channel that it must satisfy under non-error conditions.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      long average
      Get the average interval, in milliseconds, that messages will be available from a Channel; in NDN implementations, this may be used as the polling frequency for a StreamChannel.
      long maximum
      Get the maximum interval, in milliseconds, between messages from a Channel.
      long minimum
      Get the minimum interval, in milliseconds, between messages from a Channel.
